TO THE LEFT:

My first of hopefully many from PixelHead.

"Hey @elonmusk, What will wine from #Mars taste like?"

The question has been posed:
https://twitter.com/PixelHeadStudio/status/1331328939516686337?s=20

Response:
radio silence...

Maybe some day, within our lifetime, we will celebrating our societal and technological successes over a bottle of Mars Wine. Until then, my mind will genuinely be wondering, "What in hell does wine from Mars taste like!?!"

I proclaim this artwork to be a mere time capsule containing, with lack of better words, a "question in a bottle."

Cheers friends,
PixelHead

TO THE RIGHT:

The Porta Portalis - 1 - canvas runner.
Another great piece by an artist know as    AKA PixelHead, I have be grateful to become friends with.
This piece presents collectors not only with a great visual but a hidden encrypted  puzzle to be seen and captured by a sharp eye. There is a hidden QR Code with in the piece.

PLEASE CLICK ON THE PIECE TO WATCH THE VIDEO AND ATTEMPT TO FIND THE QR CODES....ONCE YOU CLICK EXPAND TO A FULL SCREEN VIEW AND ENJOY :)
